---
title: Greek Goddess Salmon & Quinoa Bowls with Roasted Chickpeas, Harissa Hummus & Cucumber Feta Salad
description: This Greek-inspired bowl stars roasted chickpeas and onions, a refreshing tomato-cucumber salad, tangy Greek vinaigrette, and briny feta cheese over nutty, nutritious quinoa (a seed-like grain that cooks up fluffy, savory, and satisfying). Adding a final flourish are smoky harissa-infused hummus and herbaceous chopped dill, completing this un-bowl-ievably flavorful meal.
